{"tid":883819,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵：西九龍站票務系統與中國相連　電腦傳輸系統不穩","createTime":"2018-10-31T06:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T07:10:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0405004049ee5e4f9964e87e827bd9692493d538","tid":883819,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181031/s00001/d3faa762e33c5beffbb4aa671025ee4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181031%2Fs00001%2Fd3faa762e33c5beffbb4aa671025ee4f.jpg&h=b5ac09a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通車約一個月的高鐵香港段，港鐵早上約9時通知其西九龍站票務系統發生故障，影響站內部分設施與設備運作，並需以人手售票及取票，至早上約10時15分回復正常。港鐵車務營運總管李聖基中午表示，由於香港票務系統與內地一方相連，其間出現電腦傳輸系統不穩定，從而影響售票系統，將與內地單位跟進和改善。<br />\n<br />\n李聖基指出，港鐵早上8時25分發現系統有問題，即時啟動應變安排，並改用人手售票，秩序大致良好；直至早上約9時45分啟用備用系統，正常出售西九龍至福田和深圳北站的車票；在10時15分，系統經內地相關單位協助後恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，其間12306系統沒有受影響，亦看不到有受黑客入侵的迹象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181031/s00001/1540960425558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181031%2Fs00001%2F1540960425558&d=THuf5Gc%2FlHAsI2zGJgWxllzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=33306055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181031%2Fs00001%2F1540960425558&h=ca5e4233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181031/s00001/1540960425558</a>"},{"pid":"bec5e7d1b991d85fbfa777a2dee8817e72acedc1","tid":883819,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"係咪因為要用vpn呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ebb7ca0d30ebfecd866df42b4815a6b971f077","tid":883819,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"即係唔連大陸就唔會唔穩定? <img src=\"/assets